lead_paragraph: The State University of New York at Geneseo’s pursuit of its first N.C.A.A. Division III title came to a halt with a 5-1 drubbing by Wisconsin-Stevens Point in the semifinals in Lake Placid, N.Y.

headline.main: Geneseo Falls to Wisconsin-Stevens Point in Semifinals
